<i>I took on my friend's face.</i>

628
00:48:57,518 --> 00:48:59,520
Along with my face and name…

629
00:49:02,357 --> 00:49:03,816
even my voice changed.

630
00:49:05,276 --> 00:49:07,195
And I had to live in the world again…

631
00:49:09,906 --> 00:49:11,240
as Paek Jun-beom.

632
00:49:13,326 --> 00:49:17,455
When I came back,
I realized how stupid it all was.

633
00:49:18,665 --> 00:49:21,334
You didn't care at all
whether I lived or died.

634
00:49:21,417 --> 00:49:23,378
[laughs]

635
00:49:23,461 --> 00:49:25,505
Did you really like money that much?

636
00:49:25,588 --> 00:49:28,132
Enough to go to a hotel with some old man?

637
00:49:29,050 --> 00:49:30,468
That was work.

638
00:49:30,551 --> 00:49:33,346
It wasn't anything like
what you're thinking… [sighs]

639
00:49:34,472 --> 00:49:36,307
So what are you doing here now?

640
00:49:36,391 --> 00:49:39,811
The Lee Su-ho you dumped
was utterly pathetic,

641
00:49:40,353 --> 00:49:42,730
but Paek Jun-beom's life was different.

642
00:49:56,077 --> 00:49:58,121
This is the private viewing room
of our auction house.

643
00:49:58,204 --> 00:50:00,123
I'll escort you inside, sir.

644
00:50:06,212 --> 00:50:08,923
[Seol-ah] Bidder number 86, 3.7 million.

645
00:50:09,674 --> 00:50:11,426
Congratulations.

646
00:50:16,806 --> 00:50:19,559
[Jun-beom] <i>So this is how</i>
<i>sweet and comfortable success is.</i>

647
00:50:20,351 --> 00:50:21,811
It makes you confident.

648
00:50:23,146 --> 00:50:24,814
I just didn't know that world.

649
00:50:24,897 --> 00:50:26,149
And then

650
00:50:26,858 --> 00:50:28,359
I started wondering…

651
00:50:32,280 --> 00:50:35,783
"With this much money,
wouldn't I be able to tempt her?"

652
00:50:37,994 --> 00:50:41,664
But part of me was hoping
you wouldn't fall for it.

653
00:50:44,375 --> 00:50:45,376
[breathes shakily]

654
00:50:46,961 --> 00:50:47,962
[breathing shakily]

655
00:50:48,755 --> 00:50:52,717
You really are Lee Su-ho.

656
00:50:54,010 --> 00:50:55,762
Lee Su-ho the fool.

657
00:50:57,638 --> 00:51:00,975
When you have nothing, the only thing
you can throw away is yourself.

658
00:51:01,642 --> 00:51:04,061
I hated you as much as I loved you.

659
00:51:04,854 --> 00:51:08,608
I wanted revenge, even if
it meant dying. [breathing heavily]

660
00:51:10,109 --> 00:51:12,069
[Woo-seok]
I'm at Paek Jun-beom's house. [grunts]

661
00:51:12,153 --> 00:51:13,613
Shit. [breathes heavily]

662
00:51:14,655 --> 00:51:16,824
I can't reach either of them.
Track their location.

663
00:51:16,908 --> 00:51:18,493
You need to move now!

664
00:51:19,660 --> 00:51:21,245
Don't you know Captain Pyo?

665
00:51:21,329 --> 00:51:23,748
You know he won't roll out
for something like that.

666
00:51:23,831 --> 00:51:25,249
What's going on?

667
00:51:25,333 --> 00:51:28,127
I don't have time to explain.
[breathing heavily]

668
00:51:28,920 --> 00:51:31,088
Then tell him to come
and arrest me in the act.

669
00:51:31,172 --> 00:51:32,548
What are you going to do?

670
00:51:33,257 --> 00:51:35,176
I'm going to kill Paek Jun-beom.

671
00:51:36,135 --> 00:51:37,762
- [Gong] <i>Hey, Cha Woo-seok!</i>
- [phone beeps]

672
00:51:37,845 --> 00:51:39,722
[sighs] Shit.

673
00:51:45,228 --> 00:51:47,230
[alarm blaring]

674
00:51:49,357 --> 00:51:51,359
[breathing heavily]

675
00:52:07,834 --> 00:52:09,126
[grunts]

676
00:52:11,254 --> 00:52:13,673
[grunting]

677
00:52:30,940 --> 00:52:32,358
APPROACHED SEOL-AH
AFTER KIM YUN-JI CASE

678
00:52:32,441 --> 00:52:33,442
FAINTED AT TAEMYUNG
ART CENTER

679
00:52:34,735 --> 00:52:35,736
SUK-JI
OBSESSED WITH SEOL-AH

680
00:52:35,820 --> 00:52:36,904
EUN-HYUK
MORE THAN A FRIEND?

681
00:52:36,988 --> 00:52:38,781
YUN-JI - OWNED UNIT,
"ACROSS FROM SEOL-AH'S PLACE,"

682
00:52:38,865 --> 00:52:40,324
CHA WOO-SEOK RESIGNED

683
00:52:41,492 --> 00:52:42,618
2024 TO 2025
ROMANCE & PROPOSAL

684
00:52:42,702 --> 00:52:43,703
DATED, THEN PROPOSED

685
00:52:43,786 --> 00:52:45,037
YOON SEUNG-JAE
RAN GALLERY RESTAURANT

686
00:52:52,253 --> 00:52:53,504
[breathes shakily]

687
00:52:53,588 --> 00:52:55,923
{\an8}HAN SEOL-AH

688
00:52:56,007 --> 00:52:57,049
{\an8}[breathes shakily]

689
00:52:57,550 --> 00:52:58,634
SEOL-AH AFTER WORK
NOT AS ME…

690
00:52:58,718 --> 00:53:00,011
SEOL-AH
SEOL-AH RUNNING AN AUCTION

691
00:53:00,094 --> 00:53:01,762
[breathing heavily]

692
00:53:04,682 --> 00:53:07,059
And if I'd come back as Lee Su-ho,

693
00:53:07,977 --> 00:53:10,146
would you have even noticed me?
[inhales sharply]

694
00:53:10,229 --> 00:53:13,482
Only after I won that million-dollar bid
did you finally look at me.

695
00:53:13,566 --> 00:53:15,610
And when you found out
I had that Stiller piece,

696
00:53:15,693 --> 00:53:17,403
you came, wagging your tail!

697
00:53:17,486 --> 00:53:18,863
[breathes heavily]

698
00:53:18,946 --> 00:53:24,201
And like a moron,
I wavered again when I saw you like that.

699
00:53:26,662 --> 00:53:29,373
[inhales sharply] I wanted
to make you my woman again!

700
00:53:29,457 --> 00:53:31,334
[breathing heavily]

701
00:53:31,417 --> 00:53:33,169
We can be happy, Seol-ah.

702
00:53:33,252 --> 00:53:35,046
I'm Paek Jun-beom now, I can do anything.

703
00:53:35,129 --> 00:53:36,631
I'll give you whatever you want, okay?

704
00:53:36,714 --> 00:53:38,257
- You've completely lost it!
- Okay?

705
00:53:38,341 --> 00:53:40,343
[laughing]

706
00:53:41,636 --> 00:53:44,597
- Why not? Huh? [chuckles]
- [Seol-ah breathes shakily]

707
00:53:45,473 --> 00:53:46,474
What?

708
00:53:49,185 --> 00:53:51,896
Really? Because of Cha Woo-seok?

709
00:53:55,024 --> 00:53:56,859
[breathes shakily]

710
00:53:57,777 --> 00:53:59,278
You like that bastard?

711
00:54:00,112 --> 00:54:02,114
[siren wailing]

712
00:54:05,952 --> 00:54:07,161
[sighs]

713
00:54:10,247 --> 00:54:11,374
[sighs]

714
00:54:12,166 --> 00:54:13,709
DO EUN-HYUK
MORE THAN JUST A FRIEND?

715
00:54:13,793 --> 00:54:15,836
DO EUN-HYE SEEMS TO
DISLIKE HAN SEOL-AH - HOSTILE

716
00:54:17,880 --> 00:54:18,881
[sighs]

717
00:54:21,133 --> 00:54:22,510
Hurry up and decide.

718
00:54:35,147 --> 00:54:37,191
- [radio beeps]
- Get Paek Jun-beom's location now

719
00:54:37,274 --> 00:54:38,609
and deploy all units.

720
00:54:38,693 --> 00:54:39,694
[radio beeps]

721
00:54:40,820 --> 00:54:41,988
Uncuff him.

722
00:54:48,077 --> 00:54:50,079
[siren wailing]

723
00:54:59,338 --> 00:55:03,426
Last ping before the signal dropped was
866, Jicheon-myeon, Yangpyeong-gun.

724
00:55:06,554 --> 00:55:08,931
[gasps] No!

725
00:55:09,015 --> 00:55:11,684
[whimpering] Get off me! Let go of me!

726
00:55:14,603 --> 00:55:15,771
[breathing shakily]

727
00:55:15,855 --> 00:55:16,856
Stay away.

728
00:55:17,857 --> 00:55:19,817
[laughs]

729
00:55:19,900 --> 00:55:21,277
Don't do this.

730
00:55:22,361 --> 00:55:24,280
I already died once because of you.

731
00:55:25,239 --> 00:55:27,241
Why not make it twice now?

732
00:55:28,784 --> 00:55:33,539
In this life,
I'm not letting you go, Seol-ah.

733
00:55:33,622 --> 00:55:35,249
[sobbing]

734
00:55:38,502 --> 00:55:40,504
[both breathing heavily]

735
00:55:41,213 --> 00:55:43,299
Huh? [breathes heavily]

736
00:56:01,942 --> 00:56:02,943
CALLING…
HAN SEOL-AH

737
00:56:03,027 --> 00:56:05,154
[automated voice] <i>The phone you are</i>
<i>trying to reach is turned off.</i>

738
00:56:05,237 --> 00:56:07,531
<i>You will be directed to voicemail</i>
<i>after the beep and charges will apply.</i>

739
00:56:07,615 --> 00:56:08,616
CALL ENDED
HAN SEOL-AH

740
00:58:06,692 --> 00:58:07,860
Don't move.

741
00:58:53,530 --> 00:58:54,782
[gasps]

742
00:58:57,076 --> 00:58:58,077
[breathes shakily]

743
00:59:01,580 --> 00:59:02,581
[breathes shakily]

744
00:59:44,707 --> 00:59:47,042
{\an8}- Let go!
- This is a murder case!

745
00:59:47,626 --> 00:59:49,211
{\an8}Let me see her just once.

746
00:59:49,295 --> 00:59:51,422
{\an8}[Seol-ah] <i>Everyone said</i>
<i>they just pitied me</i>

747
00:59:52,381 --> 00:59:54,216
{\an8}<i>that they'd do anything for me,</i>

748
00:59:54,300 --> 00:59:58,971
{\an8}so I told them to do what my parents did,
to get insurance and die.

749
00:59:59,680 --> 01:00:01,307
{\an8}[Woo-seok] <i>If someone else was involved…</i>

750
01:00:02,057 --> 01:00:05,602
{\an8}Don't let your guard down. She's still
the prime suspect of the investigation.

751
01:00:05,686 --> 01:00:08,147
{\an8}Cha Woo-seok really cares.

752
01:00:08,230 --> 01:00:09,648
{\an8}[Seol-ah] <i>Thank you so much</i>

753
01:00:11,400 --> 01:00:14,570
{\an8}<i>for helping me and trusting me.</i>

